summary: So i'm reading moomin book (second one) and i'll do notes
body:
So i’m reading moomin book (second one) and i’ll do notes

(it’s polish translation, i don’t think it’ll be a lot different tho.)

  • Snufkin sleeps in a one room with Moomin. When Moomin wakes up from winter sleep, he notices that Snufkin’s gone. And he really hates it. I’m not really sure, but all moomin’s friends were living in one house.
  • I think Snufkin doesn’t like water, or just can’t swim. (They had to take care of a magic hat, that moominpapa threw into the river, later, Snufkin finds out that it changes water into something red. (raspberry juice)) // no, nevermind. He can
  • One time, Snufkin was gone at night, and Moomin was scared, that he’ll sleep again in his tent.
  • Snufkin can see better at night than Moomin. I think that’s just because he’s used to it, not because his father was… A cat.
  • Snorkmaiden and Snufkin were playing who’ll last longer on a cloud. That pink clouds from magic hat. Snufkin lost. (Clouds are white in a book)
  • On The Hattifatteners’ island at night Snorkmaiden was scared, so she woke up Moomin. Then, Moomin was scared so he woke up Snufkin. // Błędne koło
  • “They’ll find a new island” Said Snufkin with jealousy “Secret island that no one will never find” // pls dont go moomin will be sad
  • Snorkmainden burned her fringe so Moomin said he likes girls without hair tf mate. lmao Snork just said “you’ve gone bald, sis” damn what a brat // wait that’s a pun. Brat means brother in polish
  • So Snorkmaiden found that queen, and she gave her to Moomin. And she regrets it.
  • Am i fucking dump i’m almost finished and i just realised there’s little My
  • Fuck me if im wrong… But… Ok that’s the chapter with the Groke. And… Snork just fucking closed the door. Damn he doesn’t mess around. At night when, Groke was coming to their house. And later he wants to “buy” that thing in the suitcase
  • The groke toke the magic hat. Not the shell
  • So Snufkin is about to head out, and he made that little boats. In cartoon, he made like, one, here he made a lot and later he just fucking threw them all into the river. He’s so happy. It feels like he has more emotions. It’s kinda sad tho, Moomin is just sadly looking at him. … Moomin fucking cried tf.
  • They made newspapper. On the first page was written; “Snufkin left the valley” and then, with slightly bigger font “Moominmama lost her bag”. It’s so dramatic
  • Soo uhh. That wierd wizard came for his shit and y'know blah blah that happened in cartoon, and moominmama wished for her son not to miss Snufkin. That’s cute. (Someone mentioned that already tho, i’m aware)

Overall, it feels like Snufkin from the 1990 version (also 1969 and so and so) has a lot less feelings than book version. But i really like that new version of him, it really feels liks him!

//don’t take me wrong, there’s a lot cute moments with Moomin and Snorkmaiden also!

//sorry for my english//

Devon, She/Her, Asexual, In a state of sustained fear.
I draw stuff. Blog features material that is almost always tagged appropriately unless I mess something up. 
Commissions are currently [closed] and I do not schedule when they re-open so I cannot give you a time frame for that. Askbox is usually open for doodle suggestions,headcanons, questions, what have you. 
READ BEFORE SENDING MESSAGES!
_Please only suggest things for fandoms I have shown recent interest in. I don't plan out my interests so questions about old fandoms and if I plan to draw for them are not appreciated. I am NEVER looking for new fandoms to get into, please DO NOT suggest new series for me, I promise you I HAVE heard already, I'll mention it on my own if I care. 
FEMALE FOCUS KINK ART IS BY COMMISSION ONLY AND NOT APPRECIATED WHEN SUGGESTED!!!
 ABSOLUTELY NO PERSONAL KINK STORIES! I am massively uncomfortable with irl fetish stories from people.
Even tho I am marked as an NSFW blog I do not enjoy sex based suggestions and would appreciate if you didn't leave them. I do not like pregnancy based kinks at all and I will not draw them or discuss them.Don't ever end a message in "Thanks in advance" because I will not draw for it under implied obligations.
I am not here to teach you the intricacies of my sexuality. If you do not understand it do your own basic research instead of violating the privacy of a complete stranger. I am not my kink, do not treat me as a character.
